<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,940,1037]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
The genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Saalmuller" authorityYear="1884" box="[276,368,940,965]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Ploetzia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[276,368,940,965]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Ploetzia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was established by 
<bibRefCitation author="Saalmuller, M." box="[598,803,940,965]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" refId="ref36805" refString="Saalmuller, M. (1884) Lepidopteren von Madagascar. Erste Abtheilung: Rhopalocera, Heterocera: Sphinges et Bombyces. Im Selbstverlas, der Gesellscliaft, Frankfurt am Main, Germany, 246 pp., 6 plates." type="book" year="1884">Saalmüller (1884)</bibRefCitation>
for the single species 
<taxonomicName authority="(Mabille)" baseAuthorityName="Mabille" box="[1060,1321,940,965]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Ploetzia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="amygdalis">
<emphasis box="[1060,1203,940,965]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">P. amygdalis</emphasis>
(Mabille)
</taxonomicName>
. Amongst African 
<taxonomicName box="[246,382,975,1000]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Hesperiidae</taxonomicName>
, this is one of very few species with gregarious caterpillars (
<taxonomicName box="[1091,1316,975,1000]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Pteroteinon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="laufella">
<emphasis box="[1091,1316,975,1000]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Pteroteinon laufella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, below, is another), supporting its unique position.
</paragraph>
